<section class="problem-section">
<div class="container">
	<div class="section-label">// the problem</div>
	<p class="problem-intro">
		Skills are just markdown files with YAML frontmatter — but without tooling,
		they rot fast. Missing references, hardcoded paths, generic descriptions that confuse routing.
	</p>
	<div class="problem-grid">
		<div class="problem-item">
			<code>skill-tools check</code> catches it.
			Validates structure, lints for secrets and bad patterns, scores quality 0–100.
		</div>
		<div class="problem-item">
			<code>SkillRouter.select()</code> routes it.
			BM25 full-text search picks the right skill from thousands, instantly.
		</div>
		<div class="problem-item">
			<code>skillgen openapi</code> generates it.
			Turn any OpenAPI 3.x spec into a valid SKILL.md.
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
</section>

